name: Harpie Sisters - see description
description:
Choose one of the Three Harpie Sisters!
1. Swallow , the second siblings of the sisters also the swiftest she is the best scout out of all harpies

2. Gelatik, the eldest of the sisters- she can cast illusion and ephemeral birds to do her biddings

3. Tweety, the brawl of the sisters- she command her troops with iron fist and lots of laughter, although the youngest she is the strongest in terms of firepower
